<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na thil lopite gen ahi,
 Zion I Pathien khawpi;
 A thu suksiet kit theihloh pa'n,
 A hun siem Amah chenna'n;
 Kumsawt Suongpi a kinga chuh,
 Bangin a hun sulawk dem?

[V2]
 * Hukdamna banga ki umin,
 Na galte lau ta puon la (2)

[V3]
 2. Lalpa Zion khawpi achun,
 Lungsieta nei telsak chun;
 Khawvel in ei musit mahleh,
 Na min mai suong zing ingka,
 Khawvel kipah na abei zel,
 Alopi leh hawihna tawh.

[V4]
 * Zion chate mai ngal lo chun,
 Kipahna pha a nei puou (2)

[V5]
 3. Enin, kumsawt hehpihna 'pat,
 Tuihing luite hung pawtin;
 Na chate cheng cheng a vaka,
 A taksap lauh nau cheng bei;
 Ziebang lui chuh a luon sungin,
 Kuo a dangchaka chau ding?

[V6]
 * Kumkhuo'n lungsietna hai puo'n a,
 Lalpa a piepa guolin (2)

[V7]
 4. Amun kimvel cheng cheng achun,
 Lopina leh bitna di'n;
 Mei leh meipi a kilang ui,
 Lalpa anai tih hetna'n;
 Nicheng Manna a mau Piepa,
 A sapna hawu Ngaithapa.

[V8]
 * Hossana! Chawihatna la chuh,
 A Lalchutphah tungto hen (2)</lyrics>
<title>GLORIOUS THINGS OF THEE ARE SPOKEN</title>
<hymn_number>264</hymn_number>
</song>